title: Southland Conference Announces Week 10 TV Selections
text: Southland Conference Announces Week 10 TV Selections The Southland Conference and its television partners have announced game selections and live broadcast times for football games to be played Nov. 7. Comment Beauregard Daily News - Beauregard, LA By SOUTHLAND CONFRENCE Posted Oct. 26, 2015 at 3:15 PM Updated at 3:20 PM Posted Oct. 26, 2015 at 3:15 PM Updated at 3:20 PM FRISCO, Texas The Southland Conference and its television partners have announced game selections and live broadcast times for football games to be played Nov. 7. ESPN3 will broadcast the Sam Houston State at McNeese State game at 6 p.m. Central, available via WatchESPN.com and the WatchESPN app. At the same time, Cox Sports Television is set to carry UIW at Southeastern Louisiana with coverage available on ESPN3 outside Coxâ€™s territory. The American Sports Network will televise the Stephen F. Austin at Central Arkansas contest at 2:30 p.m. Central. By SOUTHLAND CONFRENCE Beauregard Daily News - Beauregard, LA By SOUTHLAND CONFRENCE Posted Oct. 26, 2015 at 3:15 PM Updated at 3:20 PM
